-- Qatar's Barwa Bank Appoints Steve Troop as Chief Executive, Younes as COO
-- B y   S h a j i   M a t h e w
-- 2010-09-22T09:13:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-22/qatar-s-barwa-bank-appoints-steve-troop-as-ceo-younes-as-coo.html
Barwa Bank, a unit of Qatari
developer Barwa Real Estate Co., appointed Steve Troop as chief
executive officer. Troop was previously chief operating officer
at Saudi Hollandi Bank in Riyadh.  The bank also appointed Keith Bradley as head of private,
corporate and retail banking businesses, and Amgad Younes as
chief operating officer, Barwa Bank said in an e-mailed
statement today. Bradley was previously the head of corporate
banking for HSBC Holdings Plc in the Middle East and Younes was
with Egyptian bank Banque Du Caire, according to the statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  